  "description": "Use this skill to configure and manage Field Service Lightning workforce capacity \u2014 covering ServiceResourceCapacity for individual resource caps, WorkCapacityLimit for territory-level demand throttling, and reporting strategies for capacity vs. utilization analysis. NOT for Omni-Channel capacity, NOT for FSL scheduling policy rule configuration, and NOT for FSL resource skill or preference setup (see fsl-resource-management).",
  "file_location": "skills/admin/fsl-capacity-planning",
